### Alert Management
@baseUrl = https://api.costkatana.com/api
@apiKey = your_api_key

### Create Alert
POST {{baseUrl}}/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "High Cost Alert", "threshold": 100, "type": "cost"}

### List Alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
